            "title": "盤中速報 - IET-KY(4971)大跌7.05%，報145元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>IET-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4971:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4971\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4971-TW</a>)26日10:09股價下跌11元，報145.0元，跌幅7.05%，成交735張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>IET-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4971:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4971\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4971-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為GaAs pHEMT epi wafers。InP HBT epi wafers。GaSb infrared material and epi wafers。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌4.59%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.26%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-385 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-316 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-69 張</li> <li>融資增減：-10 張</li> <li>融券增減：-29 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
